1. *Iako* je hladno, ja sam išla van. (Even though it was cold, I went outside.)
2. Ona je prihvatila izazov *iako* je bila veoma uplašena. (She accepted the challenge even though she was very scared.)
3. Oni su završili zadatak *iako* su imali malo vremena. (They completed the task even though they had little time.)
4. *Iako* je ona dobro obrazovana, ona nije dobila posao. (Even though she was well educated, she didn't get the job.)
5. On je išao na sastanak *iako* je bio bolesan. (He went to the meeting even though he was sick.)